metadata.name: Mimi | HyperCat #1
metadata.description: Mimi became the queen of the house on April 17, 2021, brought in as my birthday present. She's so royal that she needs to be fed by mom's hand or she goes on a hunger strike. My mechanical keyboard and books while I use them are her favourite seat. Loves to sleep and get annoyed by little sister Kuki. - Dancc
